    "description": "<p>\r\n\tSTEELARIS PTE. LTD.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tWe steel procurement service provider and project management company. Headquartered in Singapore, we supply and manage steel projects to the construction, offshore, oil & gas and marine industries. With a dynamic team and management, we place highest importance to our values and strive to develop our greatest asset...our people. We are forward looking company with open and transparent management policies.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>Steelaris</strong> is an equal opportunity employer and strictly believes in work-life integration. We aim to build an independent high performance team who is capable to take on complex projects and assignments both locally and abroad. At the same time, we are results driven and continuously build on the skills of our team. We believe work must be fun and the environment must be conducive for career growth.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tEmbark on this journey with us. We are the Steelaris family.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\twww.steelaris.com</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t </p>\r\n",
